title: James Taylor - Acoustic Live & Rarities Vol.1
description:
JAMES TAYLOR- ACOUSTIC LIVE & RARITIES, VOL.1

A compilation with JT Live recordings from 1969 to 1979.
Including cd covers (front.back)

mp3 files:

1.Fire & Rain-Live, 1969
2.Yesterday-Syracuse, 1970
3.If I Needed Someone-Syracuse, 1970
4.Satisfied Mind-Syracuse, 1970
5.Hush A Bye-Syracuse, 1970
6.In My reply-Berkeley, (acoustic show)1970
7.Up On The Roof- Berekely, (acoustic show)1970
8.Night Owl-Berkeley, with Carole King (piano)1970
9.Love Has Brought Me Around-BBc Concert,with Carole King (piano) 1971 
10.One Man Parade-BBC Concert, 1971
11.Wow, Don't you Know-Oakland,with Carole King (piano) 1972
12.Brighten Your Night With My Day- Carniege Hall, 1974
13.Ain't No Song-Carniege Hall, with Carly Simon (vocals), 1974
14.I Can Dream Of You-Cape Cod Colliseum,1975
15.Lighthouse-Cape Cod Colliseum,1975
16.You Can Close Your Eyes- Old Grey Whistle Test, w/Carly Simon (duet vocal)1977
17.Millworker-Saturday Night Live, 1979
18.Long Ago And Far Away- Blossom Music Center, 1979

Here you can find JT covers of two Beatles songs,also three Livingston Taylor songs: In My Reply, Hush-A-Bye and I Can Dream Of You,an early JT version of Carole King's song "Up On The Roof"

If you like this first volume, I can upload Vol.2
